      <title>문해력 이슈 #1 - &#34;팝콘 브레인&#34;</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/popcorn-brain/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 23:49:56 +0900</pubDate>
